title: #TOURNOTES WITH BRETT SIMPSON
description: Brett's about to pack up and head to Australia for the start of the 2013 ASP World Tour, which kicks off on March 2nd at Snapper. But first thing's first — a chat with Peter King and a quick surf out front at Southside HB pier to make sure his equipment is working right (spoiler alert: it is.) Brett's looking good going into 2013, so stay tuned for more goodness from the hometown hero. More #tournotes will be hitting our channel as the ASP World Tour kicks off!

asset.author: Hurley
